title: Take Two at Mulholland High
description: A sequel of epic proportions.Having overcome their past creative (and personal) differences, Chloe Winterhaven and Ali Harvist return for ongoing adventures in the theatrical hallways of Mulholland High. Having signed a somewhat questionable contract, Ali is now a full-time cast member on the drama-filled reality show, and Chloe prepares to audition for the role of a lifetime. If successful, the film might take Chloe far from home and all she knows and loves. With a series of competitive co-stars, an unforgettable Homecoming, and a nostalgic trip home to Ohio, Chloe and Ali’s fall semester is full of memorable scenes, viral videos, and extraordinary moments. There is never a dull moment on the set of Mulholland High! Don’t miss this exciting sequel to Take One at Mulholland High, and prepare yourself for further adventures of Ali and Chloe in Take Three at Mulholland High, now available.Take Two at Mulholland High is a light-hearted YA novel perfect for fans of Meg Cabot and MTV's The Hills.
author: Courtney Brandt
